# DirtOS

> DirtOS is a unified application for home gardening that facilitates planning, lifecycles, monitoring, and management of gardens of all shapes/sizes.
>

## DirtOS Development Plan

> A phased implementation plan for the DirtOS gardening application.
> Each phase has a dedicated instruction file in this directory.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Key Crate / Package |
|---|---|---|
| Core language | Rust | вЂ” |
| UI language | TypeScript | вЂ” |
| Desktop shell | Tauri v2 | `tauri`, `tauri-build` |
| Frontend framework | React 19 | `react`, `react-dom` |
| Component library | Mantine v7 | `@mantine/core`, `@mantine/hooks`, `@mantine/dates` |
| State management | Zustand + TanStack Query | `zustand`, `@tanstack/react-query` |
| Routing | TanStack Router | `@tanstack/react-router` |
| 2D canvas | Konva.js | `react-konva`, `konva` |
| 3D graphics | Three.js | `three`, `@react-three/fiber`, `@react-three/drei` |
| Solar math | suncalc | `suncalc` |
| Database | SQLite via sqlx | `sqlx` (features: `runtime-tokio`, `sqlite`) |
| Type export | specta + tauri-specta | `specta`, `tauri-specta` |
| Async runtime | Tokio | `tokio` |
| Task scheduling | tokio-cron-scheduler | `tokio-cron-scheduler` |
| HTTP client | reqwest | `reqwest` |
| Sensor I/O | serialport | `serialport` |
| Charts | Recharts | `recharts` |
| Date math | chrono (Rust), dayjs (TS) | `chrono`, `dayjs` |

